      "text": "雖然今天很忙，我還是去運動了。",
      "pinyin": "Suīrán jīntiān hěn máng, wǒ háishì qù yùndòng le.",
      "pinyin_numeric": "sui1ran2 jin1tian1 hen3 mang2, wo3 hai2shi4 qu4 yun4dong4 le0.",
      "translation_en": "Although I was very busy today, I still went to exercise.",
      "translation_ko": "오늘 바빴지만, 저는 여전히 운동하러 갔어요."
    },
    {
      "sentences": [
        {
          "text": "他雖然不喜歡吃辣，還是點了麻辣鍋。",
          "pinyin": "Tā suīrán bù xǐhuān chī là, háishì diǎn le málà guō.",
          "pinyin_numeric": "ta1 sui1ran2 bu4 xi3huan1 chi1 la4, hai2shi4 dian3 le0 ma2la4 guo1.",
          "translation_en": "Although he doesn't like spicy food, he still ordered the spicy hot pot.",
          "translation_ko": "그는 매운 음식을 좋아하지 않지만, 여전히 마라샤브샤브를 주문했어요."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
